FBIS4-41228 "drsov121_b_94019" FBIS-SOV-94-121 Daily Report 22 Jun 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Economic Issues Law Sets Ceiling on Foreign Borrowing, Lending Law Sets Ceiling on Foreign Borrowing, Lending PM2306100794 Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA in Russian 22 Jun 94 First Edition p 4 PM2306100794 Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA Russian BFN [Russian Federation Federal Law No. 6-FZ signed by President Yeltsin and dated 17 June 1994: "On the Ceiling for Russian Federation State Foreign Borrowings and on the Ceiling for State Loans Granted by the Russian Federation to Foreign States in 1994"] [Text] Article 1. The ceiling for Russian Federation state foreign borrowings in 1994 is to be set at $4.7 billion. Article 2. The ceiling for state loans granted by the Russian Federation to foreign states in 1994 is to be set at $400 million. Article 3. This federal law comes into force from the moment of its publication. [Signed] Russian Federation President B. Yeltsin. Moscow, the Kremlin 17 June 1994 No. 6-FZ
